OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774257258
OL,3,CMeningitis cases drop to 29 as more
OL,4,Cthan 8,000 vaccines handed out in Kent
OL,6,FThe number of cases linked to the
OL,7,Fmeningitis outbreak in Kent has
OL,8,Fdropped to 29, from 34 on Saturday, as
OL,9,Fhundreds of students queued over the
OL,10,Fweekend to get vaccinated.
OL,12,FThe UK Heath Security Agency (UKHSA)
OL,13,Fsaid some cases initially classified
OL,14,Fas confirmed cases have been
OL,15,Freclassified following further
OL,16,Flaboratory results and clinical
OL,17,Finvestigation.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/10
