OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774257258
OL,3,CMeningitis cases drop to 29 as more
OL,4,Cthan 8,000 vaccines handed out in Kent
OL,6,FMore than 8,000 vaccines have been
OL,7,Fhanded out since the outbreak a week
OL,8,Fago, with hundreds of students and
OL,9,Fother eligible people queuing over the
OL,10,Fweekend to receive vaccines and
OL,11,Fantibiotics.
OL,13,FAs of 12:30pm on 21 March, 20
OL,14,Flaboratory cases are confirmed and 9
OL,15,Fnotifications remain under
OL,16,Finvestigation, bringing the total to
OL,17,F29.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
