CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774257258
OL,3,CMeningitis cases drop to 29 as more
OL,4,Cthan 8,000 vaccines handed out in Kent
OL,6,FStaff at the University of Kent campus
OL,7,Fclinic in Canterbury said on Saturday
OL,8,Fthat the vaccine rollout had become a
OL,9,F"slick operation" as queues and
OL,10,Fwaiting times were significantly
OL,11,Fshorter than during the week.
OL,13,FThe Canterbury site opened at 9am,
OL,14,Fwith those close to the front saying
OL,15,Fthey had been waiting since 7am, and
OL,16,Fone reportedly claiming to have waited
OL,17,Fsince closer to 5am.
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@QO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774257258
OL,3,CMeningitis cases drop to 29 as more
OL,4,Cthan 8,000 vaccines handed out in Kent
OL,6,FThe queue, mostly made up of young
OL,7,Fpeople wearing masks and big coats,
OL,8,Fappeared to be moving much faster than
OL,9,Fin previous days and dropped to around
OL,10,F15 by about 11am.
OL,12,FStudents who arrived when the site
OL,13,Fopened were at the front of the queue
OL,14,Fwithin an hour and 15 minutes,
OL,15,Fcompared with reported four-hour waits
OL,16,Fon Friday.
OL,18,FFaversham Health Centre had a short
OL,19,Fqueue of around 20 people by around
OL,20,Fmidday on Saturday despite having had
OL,21,Fa line outside from 8am.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G4/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774257258
OL,3,CMeningitis cases drop to 29 as more
OL,4,Cthan 8,000 vaccines handed out in Kent
OL,6,FNHS Kent and Medway, which is in
OL,7,Fcharge of the rollout, said it moved
OL,8,Fstaff to focus on sites with the
OL,9,Flongest wait times during the week.
OL,11,FA spokesperson said: "Our teams have
OL,12,Fbeen working overtime this weekend and
OL,13,Finto the evenings during the week to
OL,14,Fdeliver antibiotic and vaccine clinics
OL,15,Fas fast as possible."
OL,17,FAccording to the trust, 8,002 vaccines
OL,18,Fhad been administered and 12,157
OL,19,Fantibiotics handed out in Kent by
OL,20,F5.55pm on Saturday.
OL,26,@sD@VOUwD@UO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G5/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
