CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774257258
OL,3,CMeningitis cases drop to 29 as more
OL,4,Cthan 8,000 vaccines handed out in Kent
OL,6,FStudents waiting at the Canterbury
OL,7,Fsite in the morning stressed the
OL,8,Fimportance of protecting themselves
OL,9,Fand others.
OL,11,FMaria, 22, who studies drama and
OL,12,Ftheatre, said: "I think it's important
OL,13,Fto make sure we protect ourselves
OL,14,Fbecause obviously there's been some
OL,15,Fdeaths and people in hospital.
OL,17,F"I think all of us are quite worried
OL,18,Fat the moment so it's better that we
OL,19,Fall get it."
OL,26,@tD@POUyD@AOU{D@LO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G6/10
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
