OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774257258
OL,3,CMeningitis cases drop to 29 as more
OL,4,Cthan 8,000 vaccines handed out in Kent
OL,6,FAnother student, 20-year-old Bradley,
OL,7,Fwho studies sport and exercise
OL,8,Fscience, said he had been waiting
OL,9,Fsince before the clinic opened on
OL,10,FSaturday morning.
OL,12,FHe said: "I'm just getting the
OL,13,Fvaccine, getting it done. Trying to
OL,14,Fprotect myself and people around me. I
OL,15,Fthink it's very important that we all
OL,16,Fget it done as soon as possible."
OL,18,FThere are six clinics across the
OL,19,Fcounty providing antibiotics and
OL,20,Fvaccines for eligible people.
OL,26,@tD@JOUxD@aO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/10
