PN,41608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774257258
OL,3,CMeningitis cases drop to 29 as more
OL,4,Cthan 8,000 vaccines handed out in Kent
OL,6,FTwo students have died in the
OL,7,Foutbreak: 18-year-old Juliette Kenny,
OL,8,Fwho was described by her family as
OL,9,F"fit, healthy and strong" before her
OL,10,Fdeath, and a University of Kent
OL,11,Fstudent.
OL,13,FDr Ben Rush, consultant in
OL,14,Fcommunicable disease control at the
OL,15,FUKHSA, said: "It's reassuring to have
OL,16,Fseen so many eligible young people
OL,17,Fcome forward for antibiotics and
OL,18,Fvaccination and we'd like to thank
OL,19,Feveryone involved in this effort so
OL,20,Ffar."
OL,26,@qD@AOUqD@YO]wD@NOU|D@EO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G8/10
