OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774257258
OL,3,CMeningitis cases drop to 29 as more
OL,4,Cthan 8,000 vaccines handed out in Kent
OL,6,FKent County Council's director of
OL,7,Fpublic health, Dr Anjan Ghosh, warned
OL,8,Fon Friday that "small household,
OL,9,Fsporadic clusters" could appear in
OL,10,Fother parts of the UK as students who
OL,11,Fhave travelled away from Kent
OL,12,F"incubate" the bug.
OL,14,FBut he said these would be
OL,15,F"containable" and stressed the risk of
OL,16,Finfection between individuals is low.
OL,26,@pD@POUqD@RO]tD@AOUtD@JO]wD@AOUwD@MO]
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G9/10
