FL,417,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F416A1774257258
OL,3,CMeningitis cases drop to 29 as more
OL,4,Cthan 8,000 vaccines handed out in Kent
OL,6,FDr Ghosh said it was the "most likely"
OL,7,Fscenario but outlined two other
OL,8,Fpossibilities: the outbreak remaining
OL,9,Fcontained in Kent, and the "worst-case
OL,10,Fscenario" ` which he said is "highly
OL,11,Funlikely" ` of another cluster outside
OL,12,FKent.
OL,26,@nD@ZOUnD@fO]qD@\OUrD@IO]rD@^OUsD@IO]
